title: NYC Mayor Eric Adams spent $50,000 in taxpayer funds to send migrants to Florida, Texas, China
description: The city has sent 100 families to US states and several other countries, including one as far as China. This despite Mayor Eric Adams slamming Republican governors for similar policies.
